GET /v1/health


Locked architectural decisions
/health is an operational endpoint, not part of the Execution Trust pipeline.
It does not expose Business Transactions, Policies, Decisions, or any trust artifacts.
It reports only the runtime health of the service and its infrastructure.
The endpoint is intended for load balancers, orchestrators (for example, Kubernetes), monitoring systems, and operational dashboards. It has no effect on the Execution Trust Record or business state.

